<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Mjere za=C5=A1tite od =C5=A1irenja=
 po=C5=BEara obzirom na vrstu
