<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">=C4=8C=
lanak 40.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Ako je postrojenje za=C5=A1ti=C4=
=87eno stabilnim ure=C4=91ajem
za ga=C5=A1enje po=C2=AD=C5=BEara raspr=C5=A1enom vodom, mora postojati mog=
u=C4=87nost odvo=C4=91enja vode, da
