<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Voda za ga=C5=A1enje po=C5=BEara m=
o=C5=BEe biti osigurana na
