></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p>&=
nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">=C4=8C=
lanak 44.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">U elektroenergetskim objektima, gd=
je na dan
stupanja na snagu ovog Pravilnika postoje stabilni sustavi za dojavu i ga=
=C5=A1enje
po=C5=BEara, a po ovom Pravilniku nisu obvezni, mogu se ti stabilni sustavi=
 ukloniti
(demontirati) u postupku utvr=C4=91enom propisima o gradnji.<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p>&=
