<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">=C4=8C=
lanak 45.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Korisnik elektroenergetskog objekt=
a je obvezan
odr=C5=BEavati u is=C2=ADpravnom stanju stabilne sustave za dojavu i ga=C5=
=A1enje po=C5=BEara sve
do njihova uklanjanja (demonta=C5=BEe).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-align:justify"><span style=3D"font-=
size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Uklanjanje (demonta=C5=BEa) stabil=
nih sustava za
dojavu i ga=C5=A1enje po=C2=AD=C5=BEara mora se provesti uz poduzete mjere =
sigurnosti
propisane za rad u takvim elektroenergetskim objektima.<o:p></o:p></span></=
p>

<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><o:p>&=
